column5: Morn,n everyone. Crisp-12 here to start the day.Make,n ice.  HAGDA.
good looking day out there  and am I going fishing  no  I have to go shopping
GO fishing, you can always go shopping Friday afternoon . . .
yes I could  I could stick needles under my finger nails too........can you say zoo
Honestly xmas shopping on the 24th isn't that bad, 90 percent of the people have already finished. Its a ritual for me every year. I prefer to panic for 4 hours versus 6 weeks like everyone else.
its more of the parking that i consider the term "zoo"  show up early to get some primo parking  and there wont be a lot of people.
The ice can wait a few more days. Theres still time to stick an arrow in a deer !
If I could I would. 4-6 ft drifts in the field where I hunt,bust a nut walking in and out with a drag no thanks. I may hit a local bush for buck only on boxing day and before the 31..GL Richy.
